title: DID I CROSS THE LINE? Freelee & Durianrider, Political Critique & Personal Defamation.
description: A lot of people genuinely do not know the information shared in this video: they hear, e.g., that I called Durianrider "insane", and they're not aware that I actually addressed his own (specific) claims that he has been diagnosed with schizophrenia --and his claims that he has cured his own condition.  That is, really, not the same as just insulting (or defaming) someone on the internet for being insane.
